Hello,
 I have just minor question about pretrained model VGG19 in your network.
 In line 151-154 of file <denchmark-link:https://github.com/knazeri/edge-connect/blob/master/src/loss.py>loss.py</denchmark-link>
  you are using weights relu3_2 twice.
 <denchmark-code>for x in range(12, 14):
     self.relu3_2.add_module(str(x), features[x])
 
 for x in range(14, 16):
     self.relu3_2.add_module(str(x), features[x])
 </denchmark-code>
 
 Doesn't it suppose to be relu3_2 for the first one and relu3_3 for next one?
